WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:11.109 align:middle line:90%


00:00:11.109 --> 00:00:14.270 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA GARR: Hi, I'm Lisa Garr,
host of Gaiam Inspirations.

00:00:14.270 --> 00:00:16.820 align:middle line:84%
Today, I invite you to go on
a journey of consciousness

00:00:16.820 --> 00:00:19.620 align:middle line:84%
with me, guided by my guest,
new generation thought

00:00:19.620 --> 00:00:21.270 align:middle line:90%
leader, Panache Desai.

00:00:21.270 --> 00:00:24.370 align:middle line:84%
Panache has been on an
extraordinary journey himself,

00:00:24.370 --> 00:00:26.580 align:middle line:84%
from being raised in
London and recognized

00:00:26.580 --> 00:00:30.920 align:middle line:84%
as a gifted healer at an early
age and then being on Oprah

00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:33.670 align:middle line:84%
and becoming a worldwide
messenger of truth.

00:00:33.670 --> 00:00:37.070 align:middle line:84%
And today, he's going to
help us with a lot of truth.

00:00:37.070 --> 00:00:37.610 align:middle line:90%
Welcome.

00:00:37.610 --> 00:00:38.630 align:middle line:90%
Thanks for being here.

00:00:38.630 --> 00:00:39.020 align:middle line:84%
>>PANACHE DESAI:
Thank you, Lisa.

00:00:39.020 --> 00:00:40.060 align:middle line:90%
It's a pleasure, as always.

00:00:40.060 --> 00:00:41.240 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It's great
to have you here,

00:00:41.240 --> 00:00:42.860 align:middle line:84%
and just to have you
with me in person.

00:00:42.860 --> 00:00:44.060 align:middle line:84%
I was saying that
to your earlier.

00:00:44.060 --> 00:00:44.820 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: I know.

00:00:44.820 --> 00:00:45.050 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: So--

00:00:45.050 --> 00:00:45.490 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Pinch me.

00:00:45.490 --> 00:00:45.930 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I know.

00:00:45.930 --> 00:00:47.200 align:middle line:90%
Look, you're in the flesh today.

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:47.650 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: There you go.

00:00:47.650 --> 00:00:48.691 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: This is exciting.

00:00:48.691 --> 00:00:49.720 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: We're doing it.

00:00:49.720 --> 00:00:52.440 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So let's talk a
little bit about your journey,

00:00:52.440 --> 00:00:55.720 align:middle line:84%
a little bit about your story
of life as a child for you.

00:00:55.720 --> 00:00:56.470 align:middle line:90%
Was it different?

00:00:56.470 --> 00:00:59.475 align:middle line:84%
Did you have a different
experience as a child?

00:00:59.475 --> 00:01:01.975 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: Life as a child for
me, in a word, was interesting.

00:01:01.975 --> 00:01:04.430 align:middle line:10%
I was born into a
spiritual family.

00:01:04.430 --> 00:01:07.280 align:middle line:10%
And they weren't religious,
but they were meditators.

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:08.800 align:middle line:90%
And they chanted in Sanskrit.

00:01:08.800 --> 00:01:10.407 align:middle line:84%
Sanskrit's a
vibrational language.

00:01:10.407 --> 00:01:11.240 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Quite often?

00:01:11.240 --> 00:01:11.781 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Mhm.

00:01:11.781 --> 00:01:13.970 align:middle line:10%
And so we grew up
with this practice

00:01:13.970 --> 00:01:17.500 align:middle line:10%
that was at the foundation or
the core of our family life.

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:20.200 align:middle line:10%
And so for the first five
years, my grandmother raised me.

00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:22.684 align:middle line:84%
And like every day, she'd
be doing her prayers.

00:01:22.684 --> 00:01:24.350 align:middle line:84%
You know, she'd be
chanting in Sanskrit.

00:01:24.350 --> 00:01:25.974 align:middle line:84%
You know, she'd read
the Bhagavad Gita,

00:01:25.974 --> 00:01:29.400 align:middle line:84%
which is a wonderful
story in Sanskrit that

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:31.400 align:middle line:84%
annotates our journey
as individuals

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:32.890 align:middle line:90%
into the fullness of who we are.

00:01:32.890 --> 00:01:34.431 align:middle line:84%
You know, and this
is the environment

00:01:34.431 --> 00:01:38.200 align:middle line:84%
that I grew up in, an absolutely
pristine vibration environment.

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:41.821 align:middle line:84%
I subsequently was completely
open, completely aware

00:01:41.821 --> 00:01:43.570 align:middle line:84%
and connected to
everything and everybody.

00:01:43.570 --> 00:01:44.100 align:middle line:90%
And--

00:01:44.100 --> 00:01:45.430 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: By the ways
you were raised.

00:01:45.430 --> 00:01:45.950 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Yeah.

00:01:45.950 --> 00:01:48.150 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So you would start off
with chanting in the morning

00:01:48.150 --> 00:01:48.620 align:middle line:90%
and--

00:01:48.620 --> 00:01:49.120 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Yeah.

00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:51.200 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And just your day
would be about prayer and--

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:51.910 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: The whole day.

00:01:51.910 --> 00:01:52.660 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: --journey.

00:01:52.660 --> 00:01:53.970 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: That's it.

00:01:53.970 --> 00:01:55.710 align:middle line:84%
You know, and even
when I got upset,

00:01:55.710 --> 00:01:58.244 align:middle line:84%
they'd put me in the meditation
room, and I'd stop crying.

00:01:58.244 --> 00:02:00.160 align:middle line:84%
You know, it was just
my favorite place to be.

00:02:00.160 --> 00:02:01.097 align:middle line:90%
It was home for me.

00:02:01.097 --> 00:02:03.180 align:middle line:84%
You know, the energy of
that room was home for me.

00:02:03.180 --> 00:02:04.670 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Most kids you put
in the meditation room,

00:02:04.670 --> 00:02:05.670 align:middle line:90%
they would start crying.

00:02:05.670 --> 00:02:06.492 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Yeah.

00:02:06.492 --> 00:02:07.950 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So when
you went to school,

00:02:07.950 --> 00:02:09.364 align:middle line:84%
did you have a
similar experience

00:02:09.364 --> 00:02:10.530 align:middle line:90%
where you carried that over?

00:02:10.530 --> 00:02:12.037 align:middle line:84%
Or was it difficult
when you were

00:02:12.037 --> 00:02:13.370 align:middle line:90%
interacting with the other kids?

00:02:13.370 --> 00:02:14.710 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: Well, as I
got older, I began

00:02:14.710 --> 00:02:16.130 align:middle line:90%
to realize that I was different.

00:02:16.130 --> 00:02:17.762 align:middle line:84%
But I made myself
wrong for that.

00:02:17.762 --> 00:02:19.470 align:middle line:84%
You know, I was really
feeling everything

00:02:19.470 --> 00:02:20.803 align:middle line:90%
that everyone was going through.

00:02:20.803 --> 00:02:22.880 align:middle line:84%
I was very acutely
aware of-- I mean,

00:02:22.880 --> 00:02:24.340 align:middle line:84%
I knew everything
about everybody,

00:02:24.340 --> 00:02:26.180 align:middle line:84%
and things I didn't
even want to know.

00:02:26.180 --> 00:02:26.680 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:02:26.680 --> 00:02:28.515 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: And it was
hard for me to navigate

00:02:28.515 --> 00:02:30.000 align:middle line:84%
that, especially in
the teenage years,

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:31.416 align:middle line:84%
because we get to
a point where we

00:02:31.416 --> 00:02:34.030 align:middle line:84%
want to assert our
dominance, especially boys.

00:02:34.030 --> 00:02:36.170 align:middle line:84%
And you know, I didn't
want any part of that.

00:02:36.170 --> 00:02:37.740 align:middle line:84%
I just went out with all
the nice-looking girls

00:02:37.740 --> 00:02:39.448 align:middle line:84%
while everyone was
beating each other up.

00:02:39.448 --> 00:02:40.900 align:middle line:84%
So that made me a
bit of a target.

00:02:40.900 --> 00:02:42.649 align:middle line:84%
The other thing is
that I didn't subscribe

00:02:42.649 --> 00:02:43.990 align:middle line:90%
to this click mentality.

00:02:43.990 --> 00:02:45.910 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Oh, so you
didn't try to fit in?

00:02:45.910 --> 00:02:47.660 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: No, I was
this lone island

00:02:47.660 --> 00:02:49.295 align:middle line:90%
by myself, which didn't help.

00:02:49.295 --> 00:02:50.260 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Why?

00:02:50.260 --> 00:02:52.430 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: Because I just
didn't conform to any group.

00:02:52.430 --> 00:02:54.554 align:middle line:84%
I didn't feel the need
to conform to any group.

00:02:54.554 --> 00:02:55.720 align:middle line:90%
You know, I loved everybody.

00:02:55.720 --> 00:02:57.074 align:middle line:90%
I was just a part of everyone.

00:02:57.074 --> 00:02:59.240 align:middle line:84%
So you know, I didn't hang
out with the Indian kids.

00:02:59.240 --> 00:03:01.141 align:middle line:84%
I didn't hang out
with the athletes.

00:03:01.141 --> 00:03:03.140 align:middle line:84%
I wasn't hanging out with
all the academic kids.

00:03:03.140 --> 00:03:04.720 align:middle line:90%
I knew everybody.

00:03:04.720 --> 00:03:07.510 align:middle line:84%
And so that was how I conducted
myself in school and my life.

00:03:07.510 --> 00:03:09.980 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So just a second
though-- because you

00:03:09.980 --> 00:03:10.870 align:middle line:90%
said an island.

00:03:10.870 --> 00:03:13.980 align:middle line:84%
So you just kind of went between
all these different groups.

00:03:13.980 --> 00:03:16.680 align:middle line:84%
But you were OK with who
you were and who you are.

00:03:16.680 --> 00:03:17.560 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Exactly.

00:03:17.560 --> 00:03:20.260 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And that is one of the
biggest challenges for people

00:03:20.260 --> 00:03:20.760 align:middle line:90%
right there.

00:03:20.760 --> 00:03:21.150 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: It is.

00:03:21.150 --> 00:03:22.250 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Is that they're
trying to fit in,

00:03:22.250 --> 00:03:23.210 align:middle line:84%
and they get
rejected, and fit in,

00:03:23.210 --> 00:03:25.610 align:middle line:84%
and get rejected, and fit
in, and get rejected, all

00:03:25.610 --> 00:03:27.210 align:middle line:90%
throughout their whole life.

00:03:27.210 --> 00:03:31.477 align:middle line:84%
And it creates dissonance,
huge in the heart.

00:03:31.477 --> 00:03:32.060 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Yeah.

00:03:32.060 --> 00:03:34.018 align:middle line:84%
It's because most people
are living their lives

00:03:34.018 --> 00:03:35.950 align:middle line:84%
outside in instead
of inside out.

00:03:35.950 --> 00:03:36.532 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:03:36.532 --> 00:03:37.990 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: Their
informing themselves

00:03:37.990 --> 00:03:39.650 align:middle line:84%
through the voices
of other people

00:03:39.650 --> 00:03:42.330 align:middle line:84%
and through the approval or
disapproval of other people

00:03:42.330 --> 00:03:44.830 align:middle line:84%
instead of really being anchored
in the knowledge and wisdom

00:03:44.830 --> 00:03:46.621 align:middle line:84%
of who they are at the
deepest level, which

00:03:46.621 --> 00:03:48.000 align:middle line:84%
is just an infinite
divine being.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.530 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So do you
think that it was

00:03:49.530 --> 00:03:52.350 align:middle line:84%
your teachings and your
growing up through the chanting

00:03:52.350 --> 00:03:55.900 align:middle line:84%
process, or was there really
gifts that came in with you?

00:03:55.900 --> 00:03:56.400 align:middle line:90%
Which?

00:03:56.400 --> 00:03:57.010 align:middle line:90%
Chicken or egg?

00:03:57.010 --> 00:03:58.510 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: I was
really born this way.

00:03:58.510 --> 00:03:59.160 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:03:59.160 --> 00:04:01.368 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: Before I was born,
I was blessed in the womb

00:04:01.368 --> 00:04:03.895 align:middle line:84%
by an Indian saint and was
part of a whole lineage.

00:04:03.895 --> 00:04:06.020 align:middle line:84%
And everyone that we'd go
and see on the weekends--

00:04:06.020 --> 00:04:08.520 align:middle line:84%
when you're Indian, you go to
see Bollywood movies or you go

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:09.720 align:middle line:90%
see spiritual teachers.

00:04:09.720 --> 00:04:11.960 align:middle line:84%
And everyone that we'd
go and see would say,

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:13.180 align:middle line:90%
we've been waiting for you.

00:04:13.180 --> 00:04:14.550 align:middle line:84%
You know, you're here to
shift the consciousness

00:04:14.550 --> 00:04:15.310 align:middle line:90%
of the planet.

00:04:15.310 --> 00:04:16.435 align:middle line:90%
We've been waiting for you.

00:04:16.435 --> 00:04:17.500 align:middle line:90%
You have our blessing.

00:04:17.500 --> 00:04:19.589 align:middle line:84%
When you're older,
come and see me.

00:04:19.589 --> 00:04:20.970 align:middle line:90%
And this was this running joke.

00:04:20.970 --> 00:04:22.180 align:middle line:84%
It was like everyone
that we'd go and see

00:04:22.180 --> 00:04:22.930 align:middle line:84%
would have the
same conversation.

00:04:22.930 --> 00:04:24.600 align:middle line:84%
Of course, I just
wanted to be a kid.

00:04:24.600 --> 00:04:26.657 align:middle line:84%
I just wanted to watch
Airwolf or The A-Team

00:04:26.657 --> 00:04:29.883 align:middle line:84%
and hang out with BA Baracus,
who was my guru, you know?

00:04:29.883 --> 00:04:31.030 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Oh, yeah.

00:04:31.030 --> 00:04:33.560 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: You know, and just
normal, whatever that means.

00:04:33.560 --> 00:04:35.310 align:middle line:84%
But yeah, I had this
whole spiritual thing

00:04:35.310 --> 00:04:36.650 align:middle line:84%
and this whole
spiritual back story

00:04:36.650 --> 00:04:38.020 align:middle line:84%
that was always a
part of my childhood.

00:04:38.020 --> 00:04:39.120 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: And you always heard it.

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:39.920 align:middle line:90%
It was always--

00:04:39.920 --> 00:04:41.150 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Yeah.

00:04:41.150 --> 00:04:44.950 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Did somebody keep
reminding of you of it?

00:04:44.950 --> 00:04:46.187 align:middle line:90%
Did you try to deny it?

00:04:46.187 --> 00:04:46.770 align:middle line:90%
Did you want--

00:04:46.770 --> 00:04:48.670 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: I absolutely
tried to deny it.

00:04:48.670 --> 00:04:51.049 align:middle line:84%
I moved away from
spirituality in my teens

00:04:51.049 --> 00:04:52.590 align:middle line:84%
because I just got
to the point where

00:04:52.590 --> 00:04:54.630 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know what to do with
everything that I was feeling,

00:04:54.630 --> 00:04:56.610 align:middle line:84%
both inside myself
and everywhere else.

00:04:56.610 --> 00:04:59.250 align:middle line:84%
And I think at some point, I
bought into the judgment too.

00:04:59.250 --> 00:05:01.320 align:middle line:84%
You know, it's very easy
to buy into the judgment

00:05:01.320 --> 00:05:04.220 align:middle line:84%
that we have as a society of how
people are supposed to show up

00:05:04.220 --> 00:05:06.790 align:middle line:84%
and how we're supposed
to navigate our emotions.

00:05:06.790 --> 00:05:10.420 align:middle line:84%
And so I stepped away from what
I call my soul signature, which

00:05:10.420 --> 00:05:11.883 align:middle line:90%
is my own unique expression.

00:05:11.883 --> 00:05:13.466 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And how did
that work for you?

00:05:13.466 --> 00:05:14.900 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: It was awful.

00:05:14.900 --> 00:05:15.442 align:middle line:90%
It was awful.

00:05:15.442 --> 00:05:17.358 align:middle line:84%
I literally got to a
point where I just really

00:05:17.358 --> 00:05:19.040 align:middle line:84%
didn't want to be on
the planet anymore.

00:05:19.040 --> 00:05:22.042 align:middle line:84%
And I remember just crying
myself to sleep most nights.

00:05:22.042 --> 00:05:23.500 align:middle line:84%
Didn't tell my mom
and dad nothing.

00:05:23.500 --> 00:05:26.850 align:middle line:84%
I was just in this anguish,
in this existential anguish

00:05:26.850 --> 00:05:29.660 align:middle line:84%
that, of course, I didn't
understand at that time.

00:05:29.660 --> 00:05:32.280 align:middle line:84%
I knew that there was something
wrong with the version

00:05:32.280 --> 00:05:34.040 align:middle line:90%
of reality that was being sold.

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:35.540 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: But you
didn't ever register

00:05:35.540 --> 00:05:37.081 align:middle line:84%
that it was something
wrong with you?

00:05:37.081 --> 00:05:37.730 align:middle line:90%
Huh.

00:05:37.730 --> 00:05:38.580 align:middle line:90%
Throughout all the--

00:05:38.580 --> 00:05:39.955 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: Even
though people tried

00:05:39.955 --> 00:05:43.820 align:middle line:84%
to make it about me-- and of
course, judgment does that.

00:05:43.820 --> 00:05:46.490 align:middle line:84%
But at that point, I never
really questioned myself.

00:05:46.490 --> 00:05:48.816 align:middle line:84%
I always understood
that I was who I was.

00:05:48.816 --> 00:05:50.190 align:middle line:84%
And it was through
the acceptance

00:05:50.190 --> 00:05:52.380 align:middle line:84%
of who I was that I came
back to being my expression

00:05:52.380 --> 00:05:54.200 align:middle line:90%
and living my soul signature.

00:05:54.200 --> 00:05:56.010 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Was there a
moment of realization

00:05:56.010 --> 00:05:59.560 align:middle line:84%
that you had that took you
out of that place of crisis?

00:05:59.560 --> 00:06:00.310 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Oh, yeah.

00:06:00.310 --> 00:06:02.650 align:middle line:90%
I was very skeptical.

00:06:02.650 --> 00:06:06.310 align:middle line:84%
Because being Indian, you meet
lots of people who wear orange.

00:06:06.310 --> 00:06:07.940 align:middle line:84%
And not everyone's
really taking you

00:06:07.940 --> 00:06:09.689 align:middle line:84%
anywhere that's leading
you to liberation.

00:06:09.689 --> 00:06:11.750 align:middle line:84%
Some people take you
down a garden path.

00:06:11.750 --> 00:06:13.760 align:middle line:84%
And so I was very
skeptical of everything.

00:06:13.760 --> 00:06:15.890 align:middle line:84%
I never believed anything
that anyone told me.

00:06:15.890 --> 00:06:17.990 align:middle line:84%
I had to experience
it for myself.

00:06:17.990 --> 00:06:20.210 align:middle line:84%
And so even with all these
conversations with people

00:06:20.210 --> 00:06:21.960 align:middle line:84%
having about me, I
just like, yeah, right.

00:06:21.960 --> 00:06:22.585 align:middle line:90%
Leave me alone.

00:06:22.585 --> 00:06:25.020 align:middle line:84%
Why would God choose
somebody like me?

00:06:25.020 --> 00:06:26.570 align:middle line:90%
And so for me, I called out God.

00:06:26.570 --> 00:06:27.320 align:middle line:90%
I said, all right.

00:06:27.320 --> 00:06:28.980 align:middle line:84%
If you exist, then
prove it to me.

00:06:28.980 --> 00:06:30.730 align:middle line:84%
Because I'm not going
to be this messenger

00:06:30.730 --> 00:06:32.229 align:middle line:84%
that everyone says
I'm here to be.

00:06:32.229 --> 00:06:34.020 align:middle line:84%
And if I can't look at
people in their eyes

00:06:34.020 --> 00:06:36.640 align:middle line:84%
and tell them that this is the
truth based on my experience,

00:06:36.640 --> 00:06:38.280 align:middle line:90%
then I won't do it.

00:06:38.280 --> 00:06:40.630 align:middle line:84%
And so I had an
experience of the divine.

00:06:40.630 --> 00:06:44.077 align:middle line:84%
And that, for me, was the moment
where the skepticism ended.

00:06:44.077 --> 00:06:45.410 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: What was the experience?

00:06:45.410 --> 00:06:46.480 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: Just this
infinite ocean

00:06:46.480 --> 00:06:48.346 align:middle line:84%
of energy with no
beginning and no end.

00:06:48.346 --> 00:06:49.470 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Ah, where were you?

00:06:49.470 --> 00:06:50.910 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: I was In Venice,
actually, at the time.

00:06:50.910 --> 00:06:52.993 align:middle line:84%
I had moved away from
London and was in California

00:06:52.993 --> 00:06:55.600 align:middle line:84%
and I'd gone through a
really deeply cathartic time.

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:57.452 align:middle line:90%
I was no fun to be around.

00:06:57.452 --> 00:06:59.660 align:middle line:84%
Everything that I'd repressed
or suppressed or denied

00:06:59.660 --> 00:07:02.022 align:middle line:84%
about myself was
coming to the surface.

00:07:02.022 --> 00:07:04.230 align:middle line:84%
I was just going through
this amazing transformation.

00:07:04.230 --> 00:07:07.780 align:middle line:84%
So New Year's Eve of 2002,
2003, all of a sudden,

00:07:07.780 --> 00:07:10.200 align:middle line:84%
I'm here, having this
experience of the divine.

00:07:10.200 --> 00:07:12.130 align:middle line:90%
It's like the divine showed me.

00:07:12.130 --> 00:07:13.050 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: In California?

00:07:13.050 --> 00:07:13.690 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Yeah.

00:07:13.690 --> 00:07:15.130 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And what were you
doing at the time, workwise?

00:07:15.130 --> 00:07:15.756 align:middle line:90%
Were you just--

00:07:15.756 --> 00:07:16.505 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: I wasn't.

00:07:16.505 --> 00:07:19.130 align:middle line:84%
I was very blessed in the fact
that I could just kind of relax

00:07:19.130 --> 00:07:21.240 align:middle line:84%
and just figure out what it
is I want to do with my life.

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:21.740 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Ah.

00:07:21.740 --> 00:07:23.310 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: And so I
was very fortunate.

00:07:23.310 --> 00:07:25.184 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And you asked
for this though, right?

00:07:25.184 --> 00:07:26.940 align:middle line:90%
You confronted the divine?

00:07:26.940 --> 00:07:27.620 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Mhm.

00:07:27.620 --> 00:07:29.369 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And after you
had that experience,

00:07:29.369 --> 00:07:32.659 align:middle line:84%
what did you notice about
your lenses on life?

00:07:32.659 --> 00:07:34.450 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: Well, that I
was always connected.

00:07:34.450 --> 00:07:36.230 align:middle line:84%
The funny thing was that
that experience actually

00:07:36.230 --> 00:07:38.780 align:middle line:84%
confirmed to me everything that
I was experiencing as a child

00:07:38.780 --> 00:07:41.125 align:middle line:84%
but subsequently
went on to deny.

00:07:41.125 --> 00:07:42.750 align:middle line:84%
So I guess I was
always born in oneness

00:07:42.750 --> 00:07:43.980 align:middle line:90%
and always living in oneness.

00:07:43.980 --> 00:07:46.210 align:middle line:84%
It's just because most
people aren't aware of that,

00:07:46.210 --> 00:07:47.140 align:middle line:90%
I denied it.

00:07:47.140 --> 00:07:48.375 align:middle line:90%
And then I came back to that.

00:07:48.375 --> 00:07:50.500 align:middle line:84%
The other upshot of it was
everything got luminous.

00:07:50.500 --> 00:07:52.083 align:middle line:84%
You know, I talk
about it in the book.

00:07:52.083 --> 00:07:54.505 align:middle line:84%
You know, I have a moment
of just complete realization

00:07:54.505 --> 00:07:56.800 align:middle line:84%
and awakening where I'm
walking around on the street

00:07:56.800 --> 00:07:57.880 align:middle line:90%
and everything's glowing.

00:07:57.880 --> 00:07:59.291 align:middle line:90%
And I'm in Venice, California.

00:07:59.291 --> 00:08:01.040 align:middle line:84%
Venice, California
doesn't naturally glow.

00:08:01.040 --> 00:08:02.470 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: No.

00:08:02.470 --> 00:08:04.960 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: And like everything,
the graffiti, the streets,

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:06.290 align:middle line:90%
I mean, everything, right?

00:08:06.290 --> 00:08:07.600 align:middle line:90%
The whole thing was glowing.

00:08:07.600 --> 00:08:09.170 align:middle line:84%
And the light and the
luminosity that was always

00:08:09.170 --> 00:08:11.220 align:middle line:84%
present-- it's like the
true nature of reality

00:08:11.220 --> 00:08:13.290 align:middle line:90%
was revealed to me.

00:08:13.290 --> 00:08:15.690 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So you didn't--
nothing outside of you changed.

00:08:15.690 --> 00:08:17.410 align:middle line:90%
You changed.

00:08:17.410 --> 00:08:20.880 align:middle line:84%
And those things that used
to disconnect you before,

00:08:20.880 --> 00:08:24.107 align:middle line:84%
where you saw the truth, how did
you approach those differently?

00:08:24.107 --> 00:08:25.440 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: I didn't question them.

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:27.420 align:middle line:84%
I didn't question
my knowing anymore.

00:08:27.420 --> 00:08:29.565 align:middle line:84%
I didn't questioned
my truth anymore.

00:08:29.565 --> 00:08:31.010 align:middle line:90%
I stopped caring, I guess.

00:08:31.010 --> 00:08:33.115 align:middle line:84%
I stopped needing egoic
approval and acceptance

00:08:33.115 --> 00:08:34.860 align:middle line:90%
from outside of myself.

00:08:34.860 --> 00:08:36.575 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: You stopped
caring about what?

00:08:36.575 --> 00:08:39.770 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: What people had to say,
their thoughts, their opinions,

00:08:39.770 --> 00:08:41.797 align:middle line:84%
whether they liked
me, didn't like me.

00:08:41.797 --> 00:08:43.921 align:middle line:84%
You know, when I had that
experience of the divine,

00:08:43.921 --> 00:08:45.827 align:middle line:84%
there was just
complete acceptance,

00:08:45.827 --> 00:08:46.660 align:middle line:90%
absolute acceptance.

00:08:46.660 --> 00:08:49.170 align:middle line:84%
It didn't matter how
I'd lived my life.

00:08:49.170 --> 00:08:52.182 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And so you didn't care
what people thought about you.

00:08:52.182 --> 00:08:55.250 align:middle line:84%
You got to be the full
opportunity of who you are.

00:08:55.250 --> 00:08:57.420 align:middle line:84%
But what about what you
thought of other people?

00:08:57.420 --> 00:08:58.420 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Doesn't matter.

00:08:58.420 --> 00:08:59.200 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: None of it mattered.

00:08:59.200 --> 00:09:01.741 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: No, because all I could
see in them was their light.

00:09:01.741 --> 00:09:04.406 align:middle line:84%
All I could see was
who they really are.

00:09:04.406 --> 00:09:06.030 align:middle line:84%
The saddest thing
for me is that people

00:09:06.030 --> 00:09:07.404 align:middle line:84%
couldn't see that
for themselves.

00:09:07.404 --> 00:09:08.352 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Ah, yeah.

00:09:08.352 --> 00:09:09.200 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.900 align:middle line:84%
And so that is
what you teach now,

00:09:10.900 --> 00:09:15.010 align:middle line:84%
is about really seeing that
soul signature in somebody

00:09:15.010 --> 00:09:17.260 align:middle line:84%
else, in themselves,
really, in ourselves.

00:09:17.260 --> 00:09:18.020 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: Well, and
more than teaching it,

00:09:18.020 --> 00:09:20.311 align:middle line:84%
I'm very blessed in the fact
that we can experientially

00:09:20.311 --> 00:09:22.925 align:middle line:84%
deliver that to people so
that they stop questioning,

00:09:22.925 --> 00:09:24.550 align:middle line:84%
so they start owning
who they are and--

00:09:24.550 --> 00:09:25.675 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: How do you do that?

00:09:25.675 --> 00:09:28.172 align:middle line:84%
How do you experiencially
deliver that people?

00:09:28.172 --> 00:09:30.630 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: Well, this had been
happening to me my whole life.

00:09:30.630 --> 00:09:33.280 align:middle line:84%
I remember even at the youngest
ages, like five or seven,

00:09:33.280 --> 00:09:34.810 align:middle line:84%
I'd just be around
people, and all

00:09:34.810 --> 00:09:36.420 align:middle line:84%
of a sudden, all their
stuff would start coming up,

00:09:36.420 --> 00:09:38.390 align:middle line:84%
their sadness, their
anger, their fear,

00:09:38.390 --> 00:09:41.270 align:middle line:84%
their vibrational density,
everything that we've judged,

00:09:41.270 --> 00:09:43.010 align:middle line:90%
repressed, or suppressed.

00:09:43.010 --> 00:09:44.760 align:middle line:90%
And literally, they'd sit down.

00:09:44.760 --> 00:09:46.700 align:middle line:84%
They'd seemed encumbered
or burdened by life.

00:09:46.700 --> 00:09:48.630 align:middle line:84%
It's like life had gotten
the better of them.

00:09:48.630 --> 00:09:49.990 align:middle line:84%
Judgment had gotten
the better of them.

00:09:49.990 --> 00:09:52.130 align:middle line:84%
And they'd sit down with me and
they'd experience all of that.

00:09:52.130 --> 00:09:52.560 align:middle line:90%
They'd get up.

00:09:52.560 --> 00:09:53.476 align:middle line:90%
And they'd be sparkly.

00:09:53.476 --> 00:09:55.440 align:middle line:84%
That's how I'd
describe it as a child.

00:09:55.440 --> 00:09:56.950 align:middle line:84%
And I just thought it was
absolutely weird, you know?

00:09:56.950 --> 00:09:58.783 align:middle line:84%
I didn't want to hear
people's life stories.

00:09:58.783 --> 00:10:01.010 align:middle line:84%
I didn't want to know
why they hated their wife

00:10:01.010 --> 00:10:02.965 align:middle line:84%
or why they didn't
like their job.

00:10:02.965 --> 00:10:05.090 align:middle line:84%
And I'd even have moments
of looking at them going,

00:10:05.090 --> 00:10:05.864 align:middle line:90%
I'm seven.

00:10:05.864 --> 00:10:07.530 align:middle line:84%
I really don't want
to know all of this.

00:10:07.530 --> 00:10:08.029 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:10:08.029 --> 00:10:10.120 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: But my whole
life's been like that.

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:13.960 align:middle line:84%
And you know, that experience
then just solidified everything

00:10:13.960 --> 00:10:16.230 align:middle line:90%
that I'd been created to be.

00:10:16.230 --> 00:10:18.240 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So, how did
you then experience

00:10:18.240 --> 00:10:20.760 align:middle line:84%
teaching this and really
imparting this information?

00:10:20.760 --> 00:10:22.750 align:middle line:84%
At what point did
you start doing that?

00:10:22.750 --> 00:10:23.770 align:middle line:90%
Was it teenager?

00:10:23.770 --> 00:10:25.853 align:middle line:84%
>>DESAI: Well, for me it
was never about teaching,

00:10:25.853 --> 00:10:29.030 align:middle line:84%
because nobody needs
to learn anything.

00:10:29.030 --> 00:10:31.500 align:middle line:84%
If anything, we
already know too much.

00:10:31.500 --> 00:10:33.340 align:middle line:84%
So what everybody
needs to really know

00:10:33.340 --> 00:10:36.294 align:middle line:84%
is that enlightenment is an
entirely destructive process.

00:10:36.294 --> 00:10:37.960 align:middle line:84%
And what's being
destroyed is everything

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:40.890 align:middle line:84%
that you believe is false
about you, everything

00:10:40.890 --> 00:10:43.340 align:middle line:84%
that you've made more
real than the truth.

00:10:43.340 --> 00:10:46.455 align:middle line:84%
And so this energy and
this presence in the form

00:10:46.455 --> 00:10:48.580 align:middle line:84%
of the book or whatever it
is that I do is lovingly

00:10:48.580 --> 00:10:52.000 align:middle line:84%
dismantling everything that
you've accepted as the truth,

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:53.135 align:middle line:90%
but isn't.

00:10:53.135 --> 00:10:55.260 align:middle line:84%
And it all starts to fall
away until eventually you

00:10:55.260 --> 00:10:58.435 align:middle line:84%
see yourself as infinite
potential and possibility.

00:10:58.435 --> 00:11:01.240 align:middle line:84%
And you begin to see that in
you and everyone that you meet.

00:11:01.240 --> 00:11:02.880 align:middle line:84%
You begin to live
the oneness that

00:11:02.880 --> 00:11:06.320 align:middle line:84%
is available in every
moment of life and living.

00:11:06.320 --> 00:11:08.535 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Enlightenment is
a dismantling process.

00:11:08.535 --> 00:11:09.925 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Mhm.

00:11:09.925 --> 00:11:11.800 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Most people
strive for enlightenment.

00:11:11.800 --> 00:11:12.380 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Mhm.

00:11:12.380 --> 00:11:13.921 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And you say
it's dismantling.

00:11:13.921 --> 00:11:14.920 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Absolutely.

00:11:14.920 --> 00:11:19.410 align:middle line:84%
It's absolutely peeling away
everything that is false,

00:11:19.410 --> 00:11:21.830 align:middle line:84%
everything, everything that's
the illusion, our story,

00:11:21.830 --> 00:11:23.860 align:middle line:84%
our thoughts, our
beliefs, our identities.

00:11:23.860 --> 00:11:27.414 align:middle line:84%
Who are we beyond our
bodies and our minds?

00:11:27.414 --> 00:11:28.270 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:11:28.270 --> 00:11:31.340 align:middle line:84%
In most ways, our experience
of life is being trapped.

00:11:31.340 --> 00:11:33.460 align:middle line:84%
Is being feeling like
you're constantly

00:11:33.460 --> 00:11:37.060 align:middle line:90%
pushing against the machine.

00:11:37.060 --> 00:11:41.700 align:middle line:84%
And this takes the lid off of
that, allows you to kind of not

00:11:41.700 --> 00:11:44.510 align:middle line:84%
see through the separation
between yourself and things.

00:11:44.510 --> 00:11:47.050 align:middle line:84%
Even if things go wrong,
there's no separation there.

00:11:47.050 --> 00:11:47.550 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: No.

00:11:47.550 --> 00:11:48.765 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It's oneness.

00:11:48.765 --> 00:11:50.640 align:middle line:84%
That's the oneness that
you're talking about.

00:11:50.640 --> 00:11:51.430 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: That's exactly right.

00:11:51.430 --> 00:11:53.890 align:middle line:84%
And in truth, there's only
one foundational reality,

00:11:53.890 --> 00:11:55.310 align:middle line:90%
and that is love.

00:11:55.310 --> 00:11:58.544 align:middle line:84%
And that's what everyone's
being guided back into again,

00:11:58.544 --> 00:11:59.460 align:middle line:90%
but while we're alive.

00:11:59.460 --> 00:12:00.454 align:middle line:90%
That's the good news.

00:12:00.454 --> 00:12:01.870 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Let's talk
about presence.

00:12:01.870 --> 00:12:02.590 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Yeah.

00:12:02.590 --> 00:12:05.490 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So in this moment
right now with you,

00:12:05.490 --> 00:12:06.919 align:middle line:84%
there is no
separation between us.

00:12:06.919 --> 00:12:07.460 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: Mhm.

00:12:07.460 --> 00:12:08.210 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I'm there.

00:12:08.210 --> 00:12:10.320 align:middle line:84%
I'm experiencing an energy
that just is circular.

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:11.900 align:middle line:84%
And it's flowing
through both of us.

00:12:11.900 --> 00:12:12.816 align:middle line:90%
And you're part of me.

00:12:12.816 --> 00:12:13.790 align:middle line:90%
I'm part of you.

00:12:13.790 --> 00:12:16.530 align:middle line:84%
It's an incredibly
circular feeling.

00:12:16.530 --> 00:12:18.800 align:middle line:90%
But it's also boundless.

00:12:18.800 --> 00:12:20.650 align:middle line:90%
There's no separation here.

00:12:20.650 --> 00:12:26.050 align:middle line:84%
So how do you experience that
with every single person?

00:12:26.050 --> 00:12:28.180 align:middle line:90%
>>DESAI: I was born this way.

00:12:28.180 --> 00:12:30.560 align:middle line:90%
Acceptance is the key.

00:12:30.560 --> 00:12:32.997 align:middle line:84%
When you come into a profound
acceptance of yourself,

00:12:32.997 --> 00:12:35.080 align:middle line:84%
at that point, you come
into a profound acceptance

00:12:35.080 --> 00:12:36.510 align:middle line:90%
of other people.

00:12:36.510 --> 00:12:38.180 align:middle line:84%
So acceptance is the
key to self love.

00:12:38.180 --> 00:12:40.263 align:middle line:84%
And at that point, you
have been unlocked the keys

00:12:40.263 --> 00:12:44.170 align:middle line:84%
to the kingdom, because you can
love everything and everyone.

00:12:44.170 --> 00:12:45.920 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I just
saw your body drop

00:12:45.920 --> 00:12:47.220 align:middle line:90%
