00:13:00.330 --> 00:13:02.330 align:middle line:84%
Because this interview
in and of itself

00:13:02.330 --> 00:13:04.970 align:middle line:84%
has the ability to
serve as the reminder

00:13:04.970 --> 00:13:07.460 align:middle line:84%
that you've asked for
a long time ago to once

00:13:07.460 --> 00:13:09.170 align:middle line:84%
again put you back
into the forefront

00:13:09.170 --> 00:13:11.390 align:middle line:84%
of your authentic
vibrational self.

00:13:11.390 --> 00:13:14.222 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So the energy comes
through the screen, wherever

00:13:14.222 --> 00:13:15.180 align:middle line:90%
